  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the time was something, because it was four-- four children and mother and, you know, that was all the time some help for mother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One is Bulka-- name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One was Anyela.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Because, you know, not all the time the same person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because young people-- all the time young people, and some other ones, you know, really not-- These two, Bulka, Anyela, Janina, that's three I remember right now.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I finish high school 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And was, you know, the very-- very tight, very different time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we know something going on from the west, I mean, from Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Poland, was, this time, custom-- not-- not-- not only custom, that was the regular.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, young fellow who finish high school and has diploma must go for two, three months for special unit military.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Meantime, in high school, we was trained-- we go through military train, prepare to a reserve army officer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's-- I go 1939, in May, after I receive, you know, the diploma, I pass examination.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was sent to unit, where we was working physically, physically working, for two months and prepare fortification for Polish-German border.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Especially, I was sent, because I already pick up the line, technical line.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was sent to a unit, where we built forts on the border, near the river on the border, forts against the tanks, German tanks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was very interesting, construction of heavy fort, three meters thick the wall, reinforced, and so and so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we was working there two, three months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this time, I supposed to go to-- I supposed to be sent to army school for officers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This time was break the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we was-- that was the military unit, where we was.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
